Myos - Make Your Own Soup
Demo app using Vert.x and MongoDB


Requirements :
  - Install Vert.x (myos-0.1.1 uses mongo-persistor busmod. See vertx-maven-plugin for further information)
  - Specify 'vertxHomeDirectory' option in pom.xml
  - Install and run MongoDB

To run it with maven, follow these instructions to set it up : 
https://github.com/rhart/vertx-maven-plugin/blob/master/README.md
Then, use 'mvn vertx:run' to run the project



---
Note : Running myos without rebuild it :
~$ cd myos
myos$ vertx run com.excilys.labs.myos.Server -cp target/classes/
---